text: Available now! This Irvington duplex recently underwent a complete renovation, which included new flooring throughout, new kitchen cabinets, new stainless steel kitchen appliances, an updated bathroom, and ceiling fans in both bedrooms. Enjoy the spring weather on a large front porch. Also notice the large basement with an included washer and dryer. Welcome home!Pet friendly. Non-refundable tenant screening fee of $40 includes credit check, background check, and eviction report. Renters Insurance required. Accepted applicants may not have had any eviction or eviction filings in last five years. Section 8 not accepted.
